      "description": "current - This is used with the second input as described above, when you want to add a displacement to channels by using external devices or sources.\t\nWhen Active Needs Current is On, the second  input (the Active input) has an effect only if the Constant  is the current .\nWhen Active Needs Current is Off, the Constant  is affected any time the Active input is on (greater than 0).\nThis is used by the Channel Editor when editing keyframes using CHOPs. An input device like a button in the Keyboard In  or a MIDI keyboard can be fed to the Active input of many Constant CHOPs. Only the current  will be affected if this option is On.",
